TETAP WASPADA, LEGRANGE.

51
00:07:21,128 --> 00:07:22,462
PERINTAH BARUMU AKAN MENYUSUL.

52
00:07:22,546 --> 00:07:24,339
Ketahuilah, Legrange,

53
00:07:24,423 --> 00:07:27,968
Agen Argylle menuju ke lokasimu saat ini.

54
00:07:34,141 --> 00:07:36,560
Tampaknya kita melayani
majikan yang sama.

55
00:07:54,036 --> 00:07:57,331
<i>Argylle, Wyatt, rampungkan misi kalian
dan kembali ke markas.</i>

56
00:07:58,373 --> 00:07:59,374
<i>Argylle.</i>

57
00:07:59,458 --> 00:08:00,584
Matikan umpanmu.

58
00:08:00,667 --> 00:08:02,002
<i>Pikirkan baik-baik.</i>

59
00:08:02,753 --> 00:08:04,421
<i>Gunakan akalmu.</i>

60
00:08:04,505 --> 00:08:06,340
<i>Jangan percaya kata-katanya...</i>

61
00:08:14,097 --> 00:08:15,432
Kini kita sendirian.

