Tamat.

134
00:13:20,487 --> 00:13:23,198
Buku kelima selesai.

135
00:13:23,282 --> 00:13:24,616
Bersulang, Argylle.

136
00:13:43,051 --> 00:13:45,137
Ibu, pagi. Hai.

137
00:13:45,220 --> 00:13:47,306
Sudah lihat surel yang kukirim semalam?

138
00:13:47,389 --> 00:13:48,682
Aku membacanya.

139
