00:16:25,088 --> 00:16:27,382
- Seluruh nuansanya...
- Hanya...

190
00:16:27,466 --> 00:16:28,800
Sangat menyimpang.

191
00:16:29,301 --> 00:16:30,552
Baiklah.

192
00:16:33,013 --> 00:16:36,517
"Nona Li, maksudku adalah"...

