196
00:17:19,226 --> 00:17:20,561
Kau bagaimana, Alfie?

197
00:17:21,727 --> 00:17:22,980
Ada ide?

198
00:17:24,690 --> 00:17:26,023
Apa saja?

199
00:17:31,613 --> 00:17:32,781
Hei, Bu.

200
00:17:32,865 --> 00:17:35,576
<i>Hai, Sayang. Hanya ingin memastikan
kau baik-baik saja.</i>

201
00:17:35,658 --> 00:17:37,619
Aku tahu kau bisa stres
karena pekerjaan dan...

202
00:17:37,703 --> 00:17:39,454
Tolong tiketnya. Tiket.

203
00:17:40,038 --> 00:17:41,206
Tunggu, Elly.

204
00:17:41,290 --> 00:17:42,791
Apa kau ada di kereta?

205
00:17:43,876 --> 00:17:45,127
Kejutan.

206
00:17:45,210 --> 00:17:47,504
<i>Kupikir aku akan datang ke kota
untuk menemuimu.</i>

207
00:17:48,088 --> 00:17:50,382
Ayahmu akan sangat senang melihatmu.

208
00:17:50,465 --> 00:17:52,426
<i>Dan Alfie kecil, tentu saja.</i>

209
00:17:52,509 --> 00:17:54,178
Kami akan mengajakmu makan malam.

210
00:17:54,261 --> 00:17:56,972
Siapa tahu kau akan bertemu seseorang
selagi ada di sini.

211
00:17:57,055 --> 00:18:02,227
